"Assign a new :ref:`ShaderMaterial <class_ShaderMaterial>` to the newly "
"created ``ColorRect``, and set the ``ColorRect``'s anchor preset to Full "
"Rect:"
msgstr ""
"後期處理效果是 Godot 將影格算繪完成後套用到該影格的著色器。要將著色器套用到影"
"格，請建立一個 :ref:`CanvasLayer <class_CanvasLayer>`，並新增一"
"個 :ref:`ColorRect <class_ColorRect>`。將新的 :ref:`ShaderMaterial "
"<class_ShaderMaterial>` 指派給新建的 ``ColorRect``，並將 ``ColorRect`` 的錨點"
"預設設為 Full Rect："

msgid "Setting the anchor preset to Full Rect on the ColorRect node"
msgstr "在 ColorRect 節點上將錨點預設設為 Full Rect"

